graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Controller"
        Controller[modelmesh-controller<br/>Deployment]
        Webhook[webhook-server<br/>Service]
        Controller -->|serves| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Runtime Pod Architecture"
        direction TB
        RestProxy[rest-proxy<br/>Container<br/>8008/TCP]
        ModelMesh[modelmesh<br/>Container<br/>8033/8080/TCP]
        Adapter[modelmesh-runtime-adapter<br/>Container<br/>8085/TCP]
        Runtime[Model Server<br/>e.g., MLServer/Triton<br/>8001/TCP]
        StorageHelper[storage-helper<br/>Init Container]

        RestProxy -->|translates to gRPC| ModelMesh
        ModelMesh -->|routes inference| Adapter
        Adapter -->|manages| Runtime
        StorageHelper -.->|downloads models| Runtime
    end

    subgraph "Infrastructure"
        etcd[etcd<br/>Deployment<br/>2379/TCP]
        S3[S3/MinIO<br/>Storage]
        PVC[PersistentVolume<br/>Storage]
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        PredictorCR[Predictor CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ClusterServingRuntimeCR[ClusterServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
    end

    subgraph "External Integrations"
        ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        KServe[KServe CRDs]
        Prometheus[Prometheus]
        IstioGW[Istio Gateway]
    end

    %% User interactions
    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| PredictorCR
    User -->|creates| ServingRuntimeCR

    %% Controller watches CRs
    PredictorCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ClusterServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller

    %% Controller creates runtime deployments
    Controller -->|creates| ModelMesh
    Controller -->|creates| Adapter
    Controller -->|creates| Runtime
    Controller -->|creates| RestProxy
    Controller -->|configures| StorageHelper

    %% Controller dependencies
    Controller -->|stores metadata| etcd
    Controller -->|validates via| Webhook

    %% Runtime dependencies
    ModelMesh -->|coordinates via| etcd
    StorageHelper -->|downloads from| S3
    StorageHelper -->|mounts from| PVC

    %% External integrations
    KServe -.->|provides CRD definitions| Controller
    ODHDashboard -->|UI management| Controller
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| Controller
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| ModelMesh
    IstioGW -->|routes traffic to| RestProxy
    IstioGW -->|routes traffic to| ModelMesh

    %% Inference flow
    Client[External Client] -->|HTTPS/443| IstioGW

